name: Animocks (free Animated Mockups pack ) 🚀
description:
📌 Animocks

 Free animated mockups pack!!


What are the features of this pack ?!😁😎

This pack has the ability to customize the motion ... You can also adjust the color of your mocap and that it is in light mode and dark mode! 🎉🎁


This pack is going to be updated and later different sizes, different mockups and new features will be added to it !! 🚀😍


🔰This pack requires 2 plugins!

  1. ▫️ figmotion
  2. ▫️ mockup


Enjoy it and wait for pro pack! 😉👍
